  "description": "A large, dark, stocky sparrow; obviously larger and darker than Song Sparrows seen in the same area. Appeared to have all chocolate brown upperparts in shade with heavy triangular spots coalesing into lines and a spot accross breast. Heavy yellow bill, red legs and darker red feet.\u00a0 In direct light of setting sun the darkest areas were dark red-brown with grey supercillium and shoulder. The photos taken in this light of the setting sun show enhanced red on the bird and other things in photo. No vocalations were heard.",
